headline.main: South Africa's Zuma Won't Suspend Prosecutor Over Gordhan Charges
headline.print_headline: South Africa's Zuma Won't Suspend Prosecutor Over Gordhan Charges

lead_paragraph: Boeing Co has approached India's SpiceJet Ltd and Jet Airways Ltd as it gauges airlines' interest in its 737 MAX-10 aircraft, the stretched version of the yet-to-be-delivered 737 MAX narrow-body jetliner, a senior executive said.
